^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|For lead we will play "coded 10s and 9s" on this hand. If you play that, my lead of the @H10 shows either no cards higher than the 10 (very unlikely on this auction) or a broken sequence with the J (AJ109 or KJ109) - 0 or 2 higher. When partner sees dummy, he knows I have KJ10 (since dummy has the ace).|
